{"tid":2349144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"承認與炫彬戀愛中 孫藝真IG回應：「第一次因為個人的私事站在大家面前，爲什麼會這麼害羞呢？」","createTime":"2021-01-01T10:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T11:41:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34268fdaf495291dd1ab1fc740da93ba89e15038","tid":2349144,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_f92618ef4a3d5bcac72a7710b67663a4/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-01/132720-891518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_f92618ef4a3d5bcac72a7710b67663a4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-01%2F132720-891518.jpg&h=29dab4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太甜了，完全是戀愛中的甜蜜語氣！<br />\n<br />\n今天（2021年的1月1日）D社爆出炫彬＆孫藝真已經戀愛8個月。隨後，雙方所屬社承認兩人的戀情：「炫彬和孫藝真兩位演員通過作品結緣，電視劇結束後，兩人互相帶著美好的感情發展爲戀人，希望大家能用溫暖的視線來看待他們的交往，並給予支持。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4bf05bc154d556a686e877620d955126/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-01/132720-891515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4bf05bc154d556a686e877620d955126%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-01%2F132720-891515.jpg&h=77aa0d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1d73e57966b8e51a5ad34a2eca0f0f89/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-01/132720-891517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1d73e57966b8e51a5ad34a2eca0f0f89%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-01%2F132720-891517.png&h=0208dbbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午，孫藝真上傳一張花籃的照片，並寫下：「新年到了。第一次不是因為工作的事，而是因為我個人的私事站在大家面前，爲什麼會這麼害羞呢？嗯...嗯...嗯...嗯...是的，就是這樣。^.^.雖然不知道該說什麼，但我覺得應該對大家說什麼才行行..感覺好尷尬好奇怪^^;感謝能讓我遇到很好的人，會努力好好發展下去。大家給予的愛和應援一直珍藏在心底，希望在新的一年裡好事更多，祝大家健康。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_616f4afacf02ea50e9166b8d7f00ad79/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-01/132720-891513.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_616f4afacf02ea50e9166b8d7f00ad79%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-01%2F132720-891513.png&h=7095eb67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少粉絲也留言：「姊姊真的太可愛了」、「恭喜你和炫彬歐爸」、「兩人真的太配了」、「We love you sooo much」、「請一定要幸福」、「戀愛中的女人」、「太開心了，要長長久久哦姊姊」等等。大家就趁連假的時候，再去看一次《愛的迫降》啦 XD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4f7a196daa8c278c170f51bec30d11fa/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-01/132720-891514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4f7a196daa8c278c170f51bec30d11fa%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-01%2F132720-891514.jpg&h=874dd5ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7698a5c8b13e4faac7e1a311f3db2179f413f8b0","tid":2349144,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"彩：新年到了。第一次不是因為工作的事，而是因為我個人的私事站在大家面前，爲什麼會這麼害羞呢？希望大家祝福我同紋身師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3b6bef19b11959aaab5da60dd6a0d53094d6b8","tid":2349144,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7698a5c8b13e4faac7e1a311f3db2179f413f8b0","tid":2349144,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"彩：新年到了。第一次不是因為工作的事，而是因為我個人的私事站在大家面前，爲什麼會這麼害羞呢？希望大家祝福我同紋身師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"岩啊岩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1a68d68970f32edb779f786ee3953450d84f01","tid":2349144,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:45:03.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ada91414f48ef33d50a227aaad1b0a4b02ae79","tid":2349144,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3b6bef19b11959aaab5da60dd6a0d53094d6b8","tid":2349144,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7698a5c8b13e4faac7e1a311f3db2179f413f8b